  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FraudDetection团队设计一个遥感影像处理的工作流状态图。起点是FraudDetection系统发起查询，然后进入元数据查询阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "QueryMetadata"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，QueryMetadata之后会有分支对吧？一种情况是找到影像数据，另一种是没找到数据。没找到的话应该返回到LedgerService记录日志？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "QueryMetadata",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标注为\"No data found\"返回到LedgerService。如果找到数据，就进入CloudFilter进行云量筛选，这里也要有个分支——如果全是 cloudy 的情况要转到AuthVault做权限审计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CloudFilter",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Granules found",
        "All cloudy"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，CloudFilter通过后到SelectProduct选择产品，然后DownloadBands下载波段数据。这里我加一个异常分支，下载失败的话进入Error状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SelectProduct",
        "DownloadBands",
        "Error",
        "Download failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "下载成功后进入ReadRaster读取栅格数据，同样要处理读取失败的异常。读取成功的话加载为arrays，进入NormalizeReflectance进行反射率归一化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ReadRaster",
        "NormalizeReflectance",
        "Arrays loaded",
        "Read failed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "NormalizeReflectance之后是CreateComposite创建合成影像，我注意到这里有个标注\"Scaled to AuthVault\"，是说归一化后的数据要同步到认证仓库吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CreateComposite",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "Scaled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，数据要标记为scaled状态同步过去。然后CreateComposite完成后进入CalculateChange计算变化，需要Before和After两期数据都准备好。最后到Visualize生成变化图，完成整个流程回到FraudDetection。另外Error状态也要能中止流程返回起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CalculateChange",
